---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import HeroSlider from "@/components/sections/HeroSlider.astro";

const title = "Our Vision";
const customDescription = "Exploring the profoundness of human existence and our collective journey";
const customOgTitle = "The Profoundness Vision";

// Hero slider images
const heroSlides = [
  {
    id: 1,
    imgSrc: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1447752875215-b2761acb3c5d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2940&q=80",
    title: "The Human Condition",
    subtitle: "Exploring our shared journey through time",
    btnText: "Discover more",
    btnLink: "#conflicts"
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    imgSrc: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470770841072-f978cf4d019e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2940&q=80",
    title: "Beyond Modernity",
    subtitle: "Questioning the narratives that shape our thinking",
    btnText: "Learn more",
    btnLink: "#modernity"
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    imgSrc: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518495973542-4542c06a5843?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2940&q=80",
    title: "Pursuit of Profoundness",
    subtitle: "Rediscovering the depth of human experience",
    btnText: "Explore",
    btnLink: "#profoundness"
  }
];
---



<MainLayout title={title} customDescription={customDescription} customOgTitle={customOgTitle}>
  <!-- Hero Section with Image Slider -->
  <HeroSlider slides={heroSlides} category="OUR VISION" />
  
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <section class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">The Human Condition</h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#f25939] to-[#2b3579] mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 italic leading-relaxed">
          Reflecting on our shared journey and the pursuit of profoundness
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
      <!-- Table of Contents -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="sticky top-20">
          <div class="p-4 bg-yellow-50/60 rounded-lg border border-yellow-100">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <span class="mr-2 text-[#2b3579]">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle>
                  <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="4"></line>
                  <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="22"></line>
                  <line x1="4.93" y1="4.93" x2="6.34" y2="6.34"></line>
                  <line x1="17.66" y1="17.66" x2="19.07" y2="19.07"></line>
                  <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="4" y2="12"></line>
                  <line x1="20" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line>
                  <line x1="4.93" y1="19.07" x2="6.34" y2="17.66"></line>
                  <line x1="17.66" y1="6.34" x2="19.07" y2="4.93"></line>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2b3579]">Understanding Vision</h3>
            </div>
            <nav class="nav-list">
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                <li>
                  <a class="flex items-center group" href="#conflicts">
                    <span class="arrow-icon hidden w-5 mr-2 text-[#f25939]">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[#f25939] transition-colors">Human Conflicts</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a class="flex items-center group" href="#modernity">
                    <span class="arrow-icon hidden w-5 mr-2 text-[#f25939]">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[#f25939] transition-colors">Modern Perspective</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a class="flex items-center group" href="#disconnection">
                    <span class="arrow-icon hidden w-5 mr-2 text-[#f25939]">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[#f25939] transition-colors">Historical Disconnection</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a class="flex items-center group" href="#propaganda">
                    <span class="arrow-icon hidden w-5 mr-2 text-[#f25939]">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[#f25939] transition-colors">Propaganda Mechanisms</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a class="flex items-center group" href="#profoundness">
                    <span class="arrow-icon hidden w-5 mr-2 text-[#f25939]">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[#f25939] transition-colors">Pursuit of Profoundness</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a class="flex items-center group" href="#societal-structures">
                    <span class="arrow-icon hidden w-5 mr-2 text-[#f25939]">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-gray-600 group-hover:text-[#f25939] transition-colors">Societal Structures</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </nav>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <article class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
          <script>
            // Add smooth scrolling to all links
            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
              document.querySelectorAll('.nav-list a').forEach(anchor => {
                anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                  e.preventDefault();
                  const targetId = this.getAttribute('href');
                  const targetElement = document.querySelector(targetId);
                  
                  if (targetElement) {
                    window.scrollTo({
                      top: targetElement.offsetTop - 100,
                      behavior: 'smooth'
                    });
                    
                    // Update active link
                    // Reset all text styles
                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-list a span:last-child').forEach(span => {
                      span.classList.remove('text-yellow-600', 'font-medium');
                      span.classList.add('text-gray-600');
                    });
                    
                    // Hide all arrows
                    document.querySelectorAll('.arrow-icon').forEach(arrow => {
                      arrow.classList.add('hidden');
                    });
                    
                    // Show arrow and highlight text for active link
                    const textSpan = this.querySelector('span:last-child');
                    const arrowSpan = this.querySelector('.arrow-icon');
                    
                    if (textSpan) {
                      textSpan.classList.remove('text-gray-600');
                      textSpan.classList.add('text-[#f25939]', 'font-medium');
                    }
                    
                    if (arrowSpan) {
                      arrowSpan.classList.remove('hidden');
                    }
                  }
                });
              });
              
              // Highlight active section on scroll
              window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
                const sections = document.querySelectorAll('section[id]');
                let scrollPosition = window.scrollY + 150;
                
                sections.forEach(section => {
                  const sectionTop = section.offsetTop;
                  const sectionHeight = section.offsetHeight;
                  const sectionId = section.getAttribute('id');
                  
                  if (scrollPosition >= sectionTop && scrollPosition < sectionTop + sectionHeight) {
                    // Reset all text styles
                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-list a span:last-child').forEach(span => {
                      span.classList.remove('text-yellow-600', 'font-medium');
                      span.classList.add('text-gray-600');
                    });
                    
                    // Hide all arrows
                    document.querySelectorAll('.arrow-icon').forEach(arrow => {
                      arrow.classList.add('hidden');
                    });
                    
                    // Show arrow and highlight text for active section
                    const activeLink = document.querySelector(`.nav-list a[href="#${sectionId}"]`);
                    if (activeLink) {
                      const textSpan = activeLink.querySelector('span:last-child');
                      const arrowSpan = activeLink.querySelector('.arrow-icon');
                      
                      if (textSpan) {
                        textSpan.classList.remove('text-gray-600');
                        textSpan.classList.add('text-[#f25939]', 'font-medium');
                      }
                      
                      if (arrowSpan) {
                        arrowSpan.classList.remove('hidden');
                      }
                    }
                  }
                });
              });
            });
          </script>
          <section id="conflicts" class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Human Conflicts</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              We, humans, have gone through a lot. Two world wars involving seismic movement of coordinated human effort. All this effort, geared towards one action. To annihilate, what we consider as enemy — our own fellow humans.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              We, humans, despite being capable of so much and so many innovations — time and time again find ourselves at the point of conflict with each other.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="modernity" class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Modern Perspective</h2>
            <div class="my-6 p-8 bg-yellow-50/60 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
              <blockquote class="text-xl italic text-gray-700">
                "We, who define the present time with the adjective of 'modern', have imposed on ourselves a blindfold, that everything that came before us is 'out-dated' or irrelevant."
              </blockquote>
            </div>

            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              This sophisticated maneuver of the narrative that shapes the thought patterns of "modern" humans keeps us in delirium. That we never investigate the past. We accept the "modern" to be the best, and do not question it.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="disconnection" class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Historical Disconnection</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              All this to the effect, that we stay disconnected to our own history of evolution of mankind, and not assess for ourselves the architectural set-up that we humans have inhabited, has remained the same all this while, and is the cause of all the problems of the world.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="propaganda" class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Propaganda Mechanisms</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              All the propaganda mechanism that exists, and always have to be present to constantly stimulate us in wanting things that do not add to profoundness of life of humans.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="profoundness" class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Pursuit of Profoundness</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              The major impact of this, is that, we humans have been devoid of the "profoundness" that exists, and could be possible in life of human.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="societal-structures" class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Societal Structures</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              We rarely have questioned the design of the architectural premise, in which we are brought up. Be it times of monarchy, democracy, dictatorship, capitalism or communism, all innovative designs of human society...
            </p>
          </section>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
